Siren-song sorcerer Spellvis and vampire queen Natasha have reaped a valuable prize: immensely powerful auras from beings drawn to them from the universe's "end game". Now they are poised to utterly crush students Kylie and Elroy and Ooshoosh warriors Mikra and Nadesko, but for one thing: Their prey left a "scent trail" through spacetime, luring a vast, cosmic being named Feast, and if the duo use their new powers at all, they'll be utterly devoured out of all realities!
